---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Essays
permalink: /essays/
---

<p>Longform writing about independent infrastructure, the human web, intentional technology, and protocol literacy.</p>

{% if collections.essays.length %}
  {% set grouped = collections.essays | groupByYear %}
  {% for group in grouped %}
    <h2>{{ group.year }}</h2>
    <ul class="archive-list">
    {% for post in group.posts %}
      <li>
        <span class="archive-date">{{ post.date | dateToFormat("MMM d") }}</span>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  {% endfor %}
{% else %}
  <p>First essay coming soon.</p>
{% endif %}
